        "timestamp": "2018-11-20 23:09:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nYes, these rules were both existing in v13 Beijing release before the files were re-factored.\nIt is simply restoring what was lost in the re-factor. The positions of the original EdgeRules can be seen in the screenshots of the WinMerge as attached to JIRA.\nI suspect that if this is cherry-picked into Dublin, it will also require a v15 version too.",
